                        │
                        ▼
             Repeat Until Completion
                        │
                        ▼
                Final Prediction
Examples
	• Recommendation Systems 
	• Search Ranking 
	• Customer Segmentation 
	• Stock Market Prediction 

2.4 CatBoost (Categorical Boosting)
CatBoost is a Gradient Boosting algorithm developed by Yandex. It is specifically designed to handle categorical features efficiently without requiring extensive preprocessing such as one-hot encoding. CatBoost reduces overfitting and produces high accuracy, especially on datasets containing many categorical variables.
